@startuml
title Online Quiz System State Transition Diagram

initial : Initial State

state "Registered/LoggedIn" {}
state "Teacher" as T {}
state "Student" as S {}

T --> T : Create New Quiz
T --> T : Edit Existing Quiz
T --> T : Save As Draft
T --> T : Post Quiz
T --> T : View Results

S --> S : Select Quiz
S --> S : Answer Quiz
S --> S : Submit Quiz
S --> S : View Result

Registered/LoggedIn --> Teacher : Log In as Teacher
Registered/LoggedIn --> Student : Log In as Student

Teacher --> Registered/LoggedIn : Log Out

Student --> Registered/LoggedIn : Log Out

final : Final State
@enduml
